# Model routing

## Parent (planner)

- Writes: `learnings/`, `solving/RESEARCH_LOG.md`, `solving/experiments/figures/`, interpretations, plan
- Does NOT write: `submission.py` (delegate to Composer subagent)
- Spawns subagents sparingly — limited API credit
- Prior-art / web search: parent uses WebSearch (not a swarm)

## Subagents

- Model: **Composer 2.5** unless user names another
- Writes: `solving/submissions/**/*.py`, `colab/*.ipynb`, smoke-related code only
- Returns: paths, pass/fail, blockers — not long prose

## One job per spawn

No parallel subagents unless user requests. Brief = paths + contract + done-when.

## Git artifacts

Every meaningful code change lands in git (commit when user asks, or after a completed baseline). Do not leave orphan `submission.py` files untracked.
